kamu menyebabkan kekacauan besar.

71
00:05:47,366 --> 00:05:48,506
Aku punya alasan.

72
00:05:48,506 --> 00:05:49,774
Aku yakin begitu.

73
00:05:49,775 --> 00:05:51,645
