77
00:05:59,845 --> 00:06:02,215
Aku punya perasaan pribadi karena perbuatanmu.

78
00:06:02,215 --> 00:06:05,501
Jika bukan karenamu, aku pasti sudah di Broadway.

79
00:06:06,386 --> 00:06:10,400
