218
00:14:05,966 --> 00:14:07,140
Benar. Jung Woo Sung.

219
00:14:07,206 --> 00:14:09,010
Itu nama aktor tampan.

220
00:14:09,136 --> 00:14:10,350
Jung Eui Sung.

221
00:14:11,076 --> 00:14:13,250
