232
00:14:42,275 --> 00:14:43,350
Baik, Bu.

233
00:14:43,805 --> 00:14:46,020
- Apa dia pacarmu? - Tidak mungkin.

234
00:14:50,275 --> 00:14:52,020
"Kelompok Teater Tirai"

235
00:14:55,616 --> 00:14:56,691
Pak Lee!

236
00:15:01,326 --> 00:15:02,630
